
---

## 📄 5. .gitignore Estratégico

```gitignore
# Node (caso use no futuro)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Build outputs
dist/
build/
*.min.js
*.min.css

# Sensitive data
.env
.env.local
*.key
*.pem
private/
js/modules/internal/

# IDE & OS
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Logs
logs/
*.log
*.tmp

# Assets que não devem ser versionados (opcional)
assets/img/private/
assets/img/originals/

# Dependency directories
jspm_packages/

# Optional npm cache
.npm

# Optional eslint cache
.eslintcache

# Optional REPL history
.node_repl_history